headline: Alumis Stock Catapults More Than 100% As Biotech Takes On J&J, Protagonist In Psoriasis

headline: Johnson & Johnson unveils new data showing nipocalimab is the first and only investigational FcRn blocker with potential to reduce systemic lupus erythematosus (SLE) activity in a Phase 2 study
